                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Diamox - This medication is great for preventing altitude sickness. In most countries (that I'm aware of), you need a prescription for this, but you can pick it up over-the-counter in Peru."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list_item",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "1 pack of wet wipes"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list_item",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Toilet paper - In the more remote parts of Peru, the restrooms don't always have toilet paper."
                  }
                ]
              }
