          },
          {
            "type": "list_item",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Variety of snacks - I'm so glad we brought snacks! Our schedule was so packed that there were multiple times that we did not have time to stop for a meal."
