      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Overall, I was very happy with what I brought with me. The one thing I will point out is that it is not nearly as cold as you'd expect with it being winter. It gets very cold at night, but during the day, the sun is intense and moving around keeps you warm. The only reason I didn't go out and buy a puffy jacket like I had planned is because I looked at the Machu Picchu hashtag on Instagram before I left and noticed that people were wearing light jackets or short-sleeved shirts (no puffy winter jackets)."
          }
        ]
      },
