              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "https://www.loandsons.com/the-catalina",
                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ],
            "text": "Lo & Sons Catalina Canvas Weekender"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ". It is the perfect carry-on size and has just the right organizational components. As another plus, it's machine washable. I was hesitant to purchase the bag in this lighter color, but when I saw that I could just throw it in the washer, I got the dove grey color, my favorite option that they offer."
          }
